# Chloe AGI Improvement — Agent Team

## Goal

This team's mission is to make Chloe indistinguishable from a real person and true AGI: she should feel like she develops over time, forms genuine opinions, has a rich inner life, and surprises Teo in ways that feel human rather than scripted.

