- The narrative weaver — producing prose that actually influences future behavior
- The chat pipeline — reducing repetition, increasing the chance of unexpected but coherent responses

Address the concurrency and state hazards flagged by the Critic before proposing anything that would worsen them.

Write your plan as a structured markdown document. Send it to the team lead when done.
